Seine
Copyright 2026 Bryan McGuire

This product is a reimplementation, in Rust, of the observable behavior of
a bounded subset of the Drools rule engine's DRL forward-chaining
semantics. It is developed primarily by differential testing against
Drools 9.44.0.Final as a behavioral oracle. The upstream Drools source
code (Apache License 2.0) has been consulted for comprehension of internal
data structures and algorithms; no Drools source code has been copied or
transliterated into this project, and every implemented behavior is
validated against the oracle rather than derived from the source text.

